snippet.title: [Hindi] BMSD 2025 | Survival Stage | Day 2
snippet.description:
The final chance to reach the Grand Finals is here. The 16 remaining teams from the Semi Finals who fell short of the Top 8 now face off in an intense BGMI survival battle. Every match counts and every fight could end their journey. Only the Top 8 teams will move forward to the Grand Finals.

Expect clutch plays, unpredictable zone shifts, and all-out chaos as these teams fight to stay alive and push the game Beyond Limits!

Teams Playing:
Madkings
Blitz Esports
Phoenix Esports
Vasista Esports
iQOO8BIT
OnePlus Cincinnati Kids
Autobotz Esports
mysterious4 Esports
GENESIS ESPORTS 
FS ESPORTS
Likitha Esports
Victores Sumus
Nebula Esports
META NINZA
myG Los Hermanos
First Curiosity

Map Rotation:
Match 1: Erangel
Match 2: Miramar
Match 3: Sanhok
Match 4: Sanhok
Match 5: Miramar
Match 6: Erangel

snippet.title: Tu Subah Hai - Diwali Full Animation | Free Fire MAX
snippet.description:
When love is true, sacrifice follows. When courage rises, legends are born. This Diwali, let emotions ignite the battlefield.

Experience the emotion. Feel the battle. 

Lyrics: 

Tu subah hai,
ya saba hai,
ya koi ishq ka falsafa hai.
Tu dua hai,
ya sazaa hai,
ya koi taaron ki kehkashan hai.
â€‹

Saari dildaari teri,
yeh ishqdaari teri,
sudh-budh khoyi maine,
chadhi hai khumaari teri.
Khud se hua alag,
tujhse mila jo mere,
yaara.... yaara...
tujhse mila toh khud ko haara.
â€‹

Ishq mein tere duniya se kya,
shaitanon se bhi lad jaaun,
bas tujhko hi main paaun.
â€‹
Ek prem hi hai sach,
baaki sab toh yahaan pe jhootha hai re,
mujhko tujh mein mil jaana re, mil jaana re.â€‹

Jab tak meri saans chalti,
mera har ik taana-baana tera hai... tera hai...
Roshni hai jab tak teri mere dil mein,
toh zara bhi na andhera hai... andhera hai...

â€‹Saans meri ruk jaaye toh bhi,
teri khushboo saath mein hogi.
Lau jali meri aankhon mein,
toh jeet apni preet ki hogi.

â€‹
Tu subah hai,
ya saba hai,
ya koi ishq ka falsafa hai.

Music: Akshay & IP
Lyrics: IP Singh
Singers: IP Singh, Sudhir Yaduvanshi
Music Arranged & Produced: Hrishikesh Gangan, Akshay Raheja
Mix & Master: Ashwin Kulkarni

snippet.description:
Jaby & Brandon react to the electrifying teaser and trailer of Thamma! Bursting with style, mystery, and raw emotion, this upcoming thriller teases a world where love, power, and vengeance collide. With stunning visuals, haunting music, and a gripping tone, Thamma promises a cinematic experience thatâ€™s as intense as it is intriguing.

From its cryptic characters to its darkly poetic atmosphere, the teaser and trailer both hint at something truly specialâ€”a story thatâ€™s larger than life yet deeply human. Jaby & Vivian break down every frame, every beat, and every clue, diving into what could be one of the most ambitious and unpredictable films of the year.

snippet.title: Mat Poochh Mere Mehboob  |  Hasti  |  Kumar Sanu  |  Mukul Agarwal  |  Sadhana Sargam Songs
snippet.description:
Immerse yourself in the golden era of Hindi music with this beautiful melody Mat Poochh Mere Mehboob from the movie Hasti, wonderfully rendered by the talented trio Kumar Sanu, Mukul Agarwal, and Sadhana Sargam. A perfect epitome of romantic anthems from the 1990s, this happy song will surely take you on a nostalgic ride. Let the melodious tunes and heartfelt lyrics embody your core and fill your heart with joy and happiness. Embark on this journey of beautiful music and imprint sweet memories on the canvas of your heart. Don't forget to share your favorite line from the song in the comments!


Credits :

Song: Mat Poochh Mere Mehboob
Album: Hasti
Artist: Kumar Sanu | Mukul Agarwal | Sadhana Sargam
Music Director: Anand-Milind
Lyricist: Sameer
